        <h1>About Me, Web Designer and developer</h1>
        <p>I'm a full media designer and developer for your business with all kind of solutions.</p>
        <br>
      <hr>
        <br>
        <h2>Who am I</h2>
        <p>My name is Talal Emran, I'm a web designer and developer based in Ottawa, Canada. you are here because you want more about me and my interstes.</p>
        <br>

        <hr>
        <br>
        <h2>My Interests</h2>
        <p>Read and discuss the world history is my one of my favorite interests. Also, I collect stamps and coins for most of the world countries. I like to watch the soccer games.</p>
        <br>

        <hr>
        <br>
        <h2>Education</h2>
        <p>
            <ul>
                <li>Computer Operation: Syrian Institution - 1994</li>
                <li>MS Word, Excel, Access: Almamoon Institution - 1997</li>
                <li>Interactive Multimedia Program: Algonquin College - 2008</li>
                <li>HTML, CSS, JavaScript: Sololearn - 2021</li>
            </ul>
